nk:0'></div><span style='font-size:18px'>循環器・腎臓内科からの処方増</span></div></div></div><div style='flex:1;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d4a4a,#14b8a6);border-radius:16px;padding:30px'><div style='font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#a7f3d0;margin-bottom:16px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px'>見逃される理由</div><div style='display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px'><div style='display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px'><div style='font-size:24px'>①</div><span style='font-size:18px'>血糖が正常</span></div><div style='display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding-left:10px'><span style='font-size:22px'>↓</span></div><div style='display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px'><div style='font-size:24px'>②</div><span style='font-size:18px'>DKAを疑わない</span></div><div style='display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding-left:10px'><span style='font-size:22px'>↓</span></div><div style='display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px'><div style='font-size:24px'>③</div><span style='font-size:18px;font-weight:700'>診断遅延 → 重篤化</span></div></div></div></div><div style='background:rgba(255,200,50,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(255,200,50,0.3);border-radius:12px;padding:18px 28px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px'><span style='font-size:26px'>⚡</span><span style='font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:#fcd34d'>糖尿病以外の診療科でも処方が当たり前 → euDKAを知らない処方医が多い</span></div></div><div class='footer'><span>© Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
