血糖）</div><div style='font-size:60px;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:10px'>&lt;250<span style='font-size:22px;font-weight:400'> mg/dL</span></div><p style='font-size:16px;opacity:0.9'>血糖正常のまま進行する</p><div style='margin-top:16px;padding:10px 16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);border-radius:8px;font-size:14px'>血糖正常 → 見逃しやすい</div></div></div><div style='display:flex;gap:20px'><div style='flex:1;background:#fff;border-radius:14px;padding:22px;text-align:center;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.05)'><div style='font-size:40px;font-weight:900;color:#14b8a6'>pH &lt; 7.3</div><div style='font-size:14px;color:#888;margin-top:6px'>代謝性アシドーシス</div></div><div style='flex:1;background:#fff;border-radius:14px;padding:22px;text-align:center;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.05)'><div style='font-size:40px;font-weight:900;color:#14b8a6'>HCO₃⁻ &lt; 18</div><div style='font-size:14px;color:#888;margin-top:6px'>重炭酸低下</div></div><div style='flex:1;background:#fff;border-radius:14px;padding:22px;text-align:center;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.05)'><div style='font-size:40px;font-weight:900;color:#14b8a6'>ケトン(+)</div><div style='font-size:14px;color:#888;margin-top:6px'>ケトン血症</div></div><div style='flex:1;background:#fff;border-radius:14px;padding:22px;text-align:center;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.05)'><div style='font-size:40px;font-weight:900;color:#14b8a6'>2.6-3.2%</div><div style='font-size:14px;color:#888;margin-top:6px'>DKA入院中の割合</div></div></div></div><div class='footer'><span>© Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
