padding:18px 22px;text-align:center;min-width:160px;border:1px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.3)'><div style='font-size:15px;font-weight:700'>脂肪分解 ↑</div></div><div style='font-size:28px;color:#14b8a6;padding:0 8px'>→</div><div style='background:linear-gradient(135deg,#b91c1c,#ef4444);border-radius:14px;padding:18px 22px;text-align:center;min-width:180px'><div style='font-size:15px;font-weight:700'>ケトン産生 ↑</div></div></div><div style='display:flex;gap:24px;margin-bottom:32px'><div style='flex:1;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:14px;padding:22px 28px;border-left:4px solid #f59e0b;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px'><div style='font-size:32px'>⬆️</div><div><div style='font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#fbbf24;margin-bottom:4px'>グルカゴン分泌↑</div><div style='font-size:14px;opacity:0.8'>さらに脂肪分解を促進</div></div></div><div style='flex:1;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:14px;padding:22px 28px;border-left:4px solid #f59e0b;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px'><div style='font-size:32px'>🔄</div><div><div style='font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#fbbf24;margin-bottom:4px'>ケトン体の腎再吸収↑</div><div style='font-size:14px;opacity:0.8'>排泄されにくく蓄積する</div></div></div></div><div style='background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);border:1px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.4);border-radius:12px;padding:18px 28px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px'><span style='font-size:24px'>💡</span><span style='font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#5eead4'>血糖は上がらないのにケトアシドーシスだけが進行する</span></div></div><div class='footer'><span>© Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
